The paper discusses the application of the SDN paradigm in optical networks, which is a subfield of computer networking (cs.NI). The paper also covers topics related to control and orchestration of networks, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper discusses network virtualization, which is a topic in computer security (cs.SI) and computer architecture (cs.CC).
